---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy — Project Talos" description="Project Talos Privacy Policy. Learn how we protect your data and privacy.">
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-cornsilk-50 dark:bg-black-forest-950">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="bg-white dark:bg-black-forest-900 border-b border-black-forest-100 dark:border-black-forest-800">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-black-forest-500 dark:text-black-forest-400 mb-4">
          <a href="/" class="hover:text-olive-leaf-600 transition-colors">Home</a>
          <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8.25 4.5l7.5 7.5-7.5 7.5" />
          </svg>
          <span>Privacy Policy</span>
        </div>
        
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-black-forest-900 dark:text-cornsilk-50">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="mt-2 text-black-forest-600 dark:text-black-forest-400">
          Last updated: January 2026
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none dark:prose-invert">
        <div class="bg-olive-leaf-50 dark:bg-olive-leaf-900/20 border border-olive-leaf-200 dark:border-olive-leaf-800 rounded-xl p-6 mb-8">
          <p class="text-olive-leaf-800 dark:text-olive-leaf-200 text-sm m-0">
            <strong>Summary:</strong> We take your privacy seriously. This policy explains what data we collect, how we use it, and your rights regarding your personal information.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black-forest-900 dark:text-cornsilk-50 mt-8 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-black-forest-900 dark:text-cornsilk-50 mt-6 mb-3">1.1 Account Information</h3>
        <p class="text-black-forest-600 dark:text-black-forest-300">
          When you create an account, we collect:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-black-forest-600 dark:text-black-forest-300 space-y-2">
          <li>Email address</li>
          <li>Password (hashed using Argon2id)</li>
          <li>Account creation date</li>
          <li>IP address and user agent (for security logging)</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-black-forest-900 dark:text-cornsilk-50 mt-6 mb-3">1.2 Usage Data</h3>
        <p class="text-black-forest-600 dark:text-black-forest-300">
          We collect information about how you use our services:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-black-forest-600 dark:text-black-forest-300 space-y-2">
          <li>API request logs (timestamp, endpoint, response status)</li>
          <li>Code execution metadata (language, execution time, resource usage)</li>
          <li>Authentication events (login attempts, token refreshes)</li>
          <li>Device and browser information</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black-forest-900 dark:text-cornsilk-50 mt-8 mb-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        
        <p class="text-black-forest-600 dark:text-black-forest-300">
          We use your data to:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-black-forest-600 dark:text-black-forest-300 space-y-2">
          <li>Provide and maintain our services</li>
          <li>Authenticate users and secure accounts</li>
          <li>Monitor and improve service performance</li>
          <li>Detect and prevent security incidents</li>
          <li>Communicate service updates and security alerts</li>
          <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black-forest-900 dark:text-cornsilk-50 mt-8 mb-4">3. Data Security</h2>
        
        <p class="text-black-forest-600 dark:text-black-forest-300">
          We implement industry-standard security measures:
        </p>
        
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-black-forest-900 rounded-xl p-6 border border-black-forest-100 dark:border-black-forest-800 my-6">
          <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="h-8 w-8 rounded-lg bg-olive-leaf-100 dark:bg-olive-leaf-900/30 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-olive-leaf-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M16.5 10.5V6.75a4.5 4.5 0 10-9 0v3.75m-.75 11.25h10.5a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25v-6.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25-2.25H6.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25 2.25v6.75a2.25 2.25 0 002.25 2.25z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-black-forest-900 dark:text-cornsilk-50 text-sm">Encryption at Rest</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-black-forest-500 dark:text-black-forest-400">AES-256 encryption</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="h-8 w-8 rounded-lg bg-olive-leaf-100 dark:bg-olive-leaf-900/30 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-olive-leaf-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 013.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 003 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-black-forest-900 dark:text-cornsilk-50 text-sm">Encryption in Transit</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-black-forest-500 dark:text-black-forest-400">TLS 1.3</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="h-8 w-8 rounded-lg bg-olive-leaf-100 dark:bg-olive-leaf-900/30 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-olive-leaf-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.75 5.25a3 3 0 013 3m3 0a6 6 0 01-7.029 5.912c-.563-.097-1.159.026-1.563.43L10.5 17.25H8.25v2.25H6v2.25H2.25l1.5-1.5L3 18.75V16.5l2.25-2.25 1.5-1.5 1.5-1.5c.404-.404.527-1 .43-1.563A6 6 0 016.75 3.75m9 9.75h.008v.008h-.008V13.5z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-black-forest-900 dark:text-cornsilk-50 text-sm">Password Hashing</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-black-forest-500 dark:text-black-forest-400">Argon2id</p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <div class="h-8 w-8 rounded-lg bg-olive-leaf-100 dark:bg-olive-leaf-900/30 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                <svg class="h-4 w-4 text-olive-leaf-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3.98 8.223A10.477 10.477 0 001.934 12C3.226 16.338 7.244 19.5 12 19.5c.993 0 1.953-.138 2.863-.395M6.228 6.228A10.45 10.45 0 0112 4.5c4.756 0 8.773 3.162 10.065 7.498a10.523 10.523 0 01-4.293 5.774M6.228 6.228L3 3m3.228 3.228l3.65 3.65m7.894 7.894L21 21m-3.228-3.228l-3.65-3.65m0 0a3 3 0 10-4.243-4.243m4.242 4.242L9.88 9.88" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="font-medium text-black-forest-900 dark:text-cornsilk-50 text-sm">Access Controls</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-black-forest-500 dark:text-black-forest-400">RBAC with MFA</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black-forest-900 dark:text-cornsilk-50 mt-8 mb-4">4. Data Retention</h2>
        
        <p class="text-black-forest-600 dark:text-black-forest-300">
          We retain your data for as long as your account is active. Upon account deletion:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-black-forest-600 dark:text-black-forest-300 space-y-2">
          <li>Account data is deleted within 30 days</li>
          <li>Audit logs are retained for 1 year (legal compliance)</li>
          <li>Anonymized usage statistics may be retained indefinitely</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black-forest-900 dark:text-cornsilk-50 mt-8 mb-4">5. Your Rights</h2>
        
        <p class="text-black-forest-600 dark:text-black-forest-300">
          Depending on your location, you may have the right to:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-black-forest-600 dark:text-black-forest-300 space-y-2">
          <li>Access your personal data</li>
          <li>Correct inaccurate data</li>
          <li>Delete your data</li>
          <li>Export your data</li>
          <li>Object to data processing</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black-forest-900 dark:text-cornsilk-50 mt-8 mb-4">6. Third-Party Services</h2>
        
        <p class="text-black-forest-600 dark:text-black-forest-300">
          We use the following third-party services:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-black-forest-600 dark:text-black-forest-300 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Stripe</strong> — Payment processing (PCI DSS compliant)</li>
          <li><strong>GitHub/Google</strong> — OAuth authentication (optional)</li>
          <li><strong>Postmark</strong> — Email delivery</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-black-forest-900 dark:text-cornsilk-50 mt-8 mb-4">7. Contact Us</h2>
        
        <p class="text-black-forest-600 dark:text-black-forest-300">
          If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:
        </p>
        
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-black-forest-900 rounded-xl p-6 border border-black-forest-100 dark:border-black-forest-800 mt-6">
          <p class="text-black-forest-900 dark:text-cornsilk-50 font-medium mb-1">Project Talos Security Team</p>
          <p class="text-black-forest-600 dark:text-black-forest-400 text-sm mb-3">privacy@talos.dev</p>
          
          <p class="text-black-forest-500 dark:text-black-forest-500 text-xs">
            We aim to respond to all privacy inquiries within 48 hours.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
